			<td class="xar-norm author">
				<div><a href="http://www.ldonline.org/roles/25883">stac2007</a></div>
				<div class="xar-sub">
										Joined: Mar 22, 2007<br/>Posts: 1										<br /><a href="http://www.ldonline.org/xarbb?by=25883&amp;func=searchtopics">Other Topics</a>
